{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ZStack\/font(_:)"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"nonisolated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"font"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"font"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Font","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Font","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4FontV"},{"kind":"text","text":"?) -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"},{"kind":"text","text":"\n"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"font","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default font to use in this view."}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A view with the default font set to the value you supply.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"code":"font(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to apply a specific font to all of the text in a view."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The example below shows the effects of applying fonts to individual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"views and to view hierarchies. Font information flows down the view"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"hierarchy as part of the environment, and remains in effect unless"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"overridden at the level of an individual view or view container."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Here, the outermost "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack"},{"type":"text","text":" applies a 16-point system font as a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"default font to views contained in that "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack"},{"type":"text","text":". Inside that stack,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the example applies a "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Font\/largeTitle"},{"type":"text","text":" font to just the first text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view; this explicitly overrides the default. The remaining stack and the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"views contained with it continue to use the 16-point system font set by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"their containing view:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["VStack {","    Text(\"Font applied to a text view.\")","        .font(.largeTitle)","","    VStack {","        Text(\"These 2 text views have the same font\")","        Text(\"applied to their parent hierarchy\")","    }","}",".font(.system(size: 16, weight: .light, design: .default))"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","title":"font(_:)","platforms":[{"beta":false,"name":"iOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"13.0"},{"beta":false,"name":"macOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"10.15"},{"beta":false,"name":"tvOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"13.0"},{"beta":false,"name":"visio